				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=166270&amp;sid=aaed1570b21b0f9bdb733f08e6c17794#166270"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Thu Dec 09, 2004 11:39 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: EQ II - Month 1 Impressions + &quot;Macro'd to death&quot; B</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=166270&amp;sid=aaed1570b21b0f9bdb733f08e6c17794"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
