				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've only seen lag a few times since the game has gone live.  Most people I know don't consider this a problem with the game.
<br />

<br />
There probably is a lack of solo content.
<br />

<br />
I'm only level 8 crafter so I can't comment on the crafting system.  I do know turning off selling to npc merchants is only a temporary fix until today's patch.  So it lasted all of 1 day?  I'm not sure I consider it a bad thing that you can't make lots of money by crafting then selling to an NPC.
<br />

<br />
I like shared group xp debt.  If you just have a death every now and then it's of no consequence almost.  A group wipe really isn't even that bad if you actually handle it correctly instead of being dumb and racking up more deaths.  It probably sucks in lower level pickup groups but then what doesn't?  It just penalizes your group for stupid mistakes.  People will need to either learn to not be stupid in a group or not get groups.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
